{
    "text": "## Sparx Maths Settings\n\n**PDF Settings**\nAnswers  ``✅``\nQuestions  ${userSetting.pdfSettings?.question ? '``✅``' : '``❌``'}\nWorking Out  ${userSetting.pdfSettings?.working_out ? '``✅``' : '``❌``'}\n> These are the settings for the pdf provided at the end of each session and is what will be included in the pdf.\n**Fake Time**\n${userSetting.min}-${userSetting.max} Seconds\n> Fake Time is the time that the teachers will see — not how long the bot will actually take. Fake Time is **PER QUESTION**, not per homework. The recommended Fake Time is 100-140s and cannot be set above 180s to prevent getting caught!\n**Model Order**\n${userSetting.model ?? 'No Models'}\n> The order of the models that will assist you with your homework.",
